name: Akshay Patel
summary: Akshay Patel is a 28-year-old Software Engineer in the Technology industry based in Los Angeles, California. He graduated from the University of California, Berkeley, and values hard work, family, and respect for all. Akshay speaks English, Hindi, and Gujarati, and seeks a life partner who shares his love for coding, hiking, and photography. As a Hindu and liberal, Akshay intends to find a life partner through monogamous dating. Akshay identifies as a straight man, is of South Asian ethnicity, has no children but wants to have them in the future. He is an Aries with an INTJ personality type who occasionally drinks but does not smoke or use drugs. Akshay prefers an active lifestyle and seeks a partner aged between 24 to 32, who is 5'2" to 6'0", has no children but wants them, shares his state of health, and does not smoke or use drugs.
